_sText:
Map from M.I.A. Jailbreak, dated 25/02/2009.

Created by dot.rich for M.I.A. 24/7 Jailbreak.

An edited version of the famous map Electric Razor (2007), it was intended to be the "ultimate" Jailbreak map and in terms of features blows all other M.I.A. maps out of the water. This map contains an obstacle course, laser game, 2 skipping arenas, a boxing arena, a vent cell, a map secret, kitchen, ice hockey, basketball, and a vessel of other vents snaking around the map.
